{"word":"μεταμορφόω","slug":"μεταμορφόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μεταμορφόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μετά\">μετά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μορφόω\">μορφόω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> ‘undergo complete alteration’, <b>be changed<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on character and personhood (‘transformed’) <b><a href='B:520 12:2'>Ro 12:2</a>; <a href='B:540 3:18'>2 Cor 3:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on alteration of appearance (‘transfigured’) <b><a href='B:470 17:2'>Mt 17:2</a>; <a href='B:480 9:2'>Mk 9:2</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μεταμέλομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μετανοέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}